flowchart TD
    U([使用者瀏覽器]) --> MW{middleware<br/>已登入?}
    MW -->|否, 進 dashboard| LOGIN[導向 /login]
    MW -->|是| LAYOUT{dashboard layout<br/>session 存在?}
    LAYOUT -->|否| LOGIN
    LAYOUT -->|是| ROLE{角色判斷}

    subgraph 認證流程
        LOGIN --> FORM[login-form 提交]
        FORM --> AUTH[lib/auth authorize]
        AUTH --> ZOD[Zod 驗證格式]
        ZOD --> BCRYPT[bcrypt 比對密碼]
        BCRYPT --> JWT[寫入 role 到 JWT]
    end

    subgraph 資料讀取
        ROLE -->|client| OWN[只查自己的專案]
        ROLE -->|admin/team| ALL[查全部專案]
        OWN --> CARD[ProjectCard 渲染]
        ALL --> CARD
    end

    subgraph 任務寫入
        CARD --> BOARD[KanbanBoard 拖曳]
        BOARD --> OPT[樂觀更新 UI]
        OPT --> ACT[updateTaskStatus<br/>Server Action]
        ACT --> GUARD{五段越權防禦}
        GUARD -->|通過| DB[(更新 Neon DB)]
        GUARD -->|失敗| RELOAD[整頁 reload 回滾]
        DB --> REVAL[revalidatePath]
    end
